                          HISTORY

Brief version information from development. For informational purposes only.

Version     011     (and before) Hard at work creating a sane system.

Version     012     Initial Release

Version     013     Updated sound driver loading (now Intel HDA works)
                    (Intel High Definition Audio)

Version     013     Created Lite version. ComLin now fits on an 8GB USB
                    drive. Removed: some locales, Java, Texi and such.
                    The Lite version still has all the goodies like
                    Openoffice, Firefox, Thunderbird Gimp ... etc ....

Version     014     First release. (Source forge release.)

Version     015     Added extra syslin command lines for second device.
                    (SATA shows up before USB). Updated pangview for
                    Converted initramfs to custom dracut.
                    Table driven pangview parser. Tested GL based utilities
                    ... etc

Version     016     Second release. (Source forge release.) Updated Boot
                    process, Docs and version numbers in /etc/

Version     017     Converted to 64 bit, real root etc ...



